Title: MPD with MPD class of IEPD is an IEPD
Text: A model package description with an MPD class of http://reference.niem.gov/niem/specification/model-package-description/3.0/#IEPD MUST be an information exchange package documentation.

Title: MPD Class Determined by Conformance Target Identifier in c:mpdClassURIList
Text: An MPD MUST have an MPD class of a conformance target identifier if and only if that conformance target identifier appears in the c:mpdClassURIList attribute within its MPD catalog document.
